---
// Figure: Minimal verification receipt
// Sequence-style diagram showing a bounded verification event.
// Left column: actors (Holder, Checker, Relying party, Holder inbox).
// Right column: what is NOT created by the event.
// Static SVG, monochrome, standards-note tone.
---

<div class="reveal my-12 md:my-16">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.6);">
    <div class="p-6 md:p-8">

      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-1">Verification event</p>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Minimal verification receipt</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.35fr,1fr] gap-5 md:gap-6">

        <!-- Sequence column -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border/60 p-4 md:p-5" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.4);">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-text-tertiary">What happens</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-text-tertiary">t₀ → t₆</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Actor headings -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 mb-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-text-tertiary">
            <div class="text-center">HOLDER</div>
            <div class="text-center">CHECKER</div>
            <div class="text-center">RELYING<br/>PARTY</div>
            <div class="text-center">HOLDER<br/>INBOX</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Steps -->
          <ol class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">01</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Presents credential</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">holder → checker</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">02</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Requests only required claims</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">checker → holder</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">03</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Approves disclosure</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">holder → checker</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">04</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Verifies status and integrity</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">checker → issuer status</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">05</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Result returned to relying party</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">checker → relying party</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">06</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold shrink-0">Minimal verification receipt emitted</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs mt-1 leading-relaxed">
                  Checker · relying party context · claims requested · claims disclosed · result · time · event reference
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[1.25rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-text-tertiary pt-0.5">07</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-text-secondary">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Holder can inspect the event later</span>
                  <span class="text-text-tertiary font-mono text-[10px]">holder inbox</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Boundary column — what is NOT created -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border p-4 md:p-5" style="border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.25); background: rgba(239,68,68,0.03);">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(239,68,68,0.7);"></span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.75);">Not created by this event</span>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
              <span>No universal behaviour log</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
              <span>No unnecessary cross service trace</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
              <span>No open ended third party retention</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
              <span>No disclosure beyond the claims the use case requires</span>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[0.9rem,1fr] gap-2 items-start">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: rgba(239,68,68,0.6);">−</span>
              <span>No profile surface visible to other relying parties</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-border/40">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-text-tertiary mb-2">Receipt is</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Narrow, purpose bound, visible to the holder first, retained only for the legally justified window, scoped to dispute and compliance use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs mt-3 text-center italic">
    Replayable verification requires a minimal receipt, not just a pass or fail. The receipt is the evidence a dispute or audit can reach for later.
  </p>
</div>
